807
01:14:50.992 --> 01:14:55.093
Still. it's the neural pathway of least resistance.

808
01:14:59.100 --> 01:15:00.401
The one I made.

809
01:15:00.936 --> 01:15:02.370
The one that kept me safe...

810
01:15:02.904 --> 01:15:04.338
when I was a child.

811
01:15:06.241 --> 01:15:07.840
You know...

812
01:15:10.111 --> 01:15:12.351
I learned to push people away before they could hurt me.

813
01:15:13.448 --> 01:15:16.384
And. now. as an adult.

814
01:15:17.285 --> 01:15:20.954
